            {
              "message": "D5 states that `verify-*` Docker reproducibility gates remain as `cargo make` entry points, but D7 later says the public `verify-doc-links` wrapper should be deleted and only the internal dependency retained. Since `verify-doc-links` is itself a `verify-*` task, the plan gives conflicting implementation requirements unless D5 excludes this task or D7 is explicitly marked as an exception.",
