        {
          "type": "fast",
          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "D9 conflates `.harness/config/dry-check.json` as both the source of truth for the DRY threshold and a historical record whose `threshold` value should not affect the next decision. Those roles conflict in the same file/field, so the implementation boundary is ambiguous unless config and history are split or the wording is tightened.",
